python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.9
  * Network and QuakeLive service error workaround.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.8
  * setup.py now has fixed requirements.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.7
  * Refactored connect method to be able to connect to quakelive service without connecting to xmpp service.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.6
  * Added user agent to make users connect successfully after quakelive's ddos.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.5
  * Ability to obtain map database from quakelive network.
  * Deleted shared using of QLNetwork.instance variable, now it uses singleton.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.4
  * Fixed exception while obtaining user stats.
  * Implemented nick name existing check.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.3
  * Fixed bug when non-pro players could not connect to quakelive network.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.2
  * QuakeLive profile summary information parsing.

python3-qllauncher 0.6.1.1
  * Added ability to obtain live streams from twitch.tv.
  * Initial profile view.
